<p>Syntax for your content:</p>

<pre class="rs-js-code-quote rs-box-code">&lt;module&gt;
{
	"LazyLoad":
	{
		"src": "images/redaxscript.png",
		"options":
		{
			"class": "rs-image rs-image-default",
			"alt": "Alternative text for image"
		}
	}
}
&lt;/module&gt;</pre>

<p>Syntax to multiserve images according to device:</p>

<pre class="rs-js-code-quote rs-box-code">&lt;module&gt;
{
	"LazyLoad":
	{
		"src":
		{
			"desktop": "images/redaxscript_desktop.png",
			"tablet": "images/redaxscript_tablet.png",
			"mobile": "images/redaxscript_mobile.png"
		}
	}
}
&lt;/module&gt;</pre>